123	    '     This is the single most common false positive. Look for it first.',
124	    '  3. HTML and technical vocabulary is not site content. A slot tag, a frame tag, a script filename: never evidence.',
125	    '  4. For an ABSENCE claim, "no_breach" means the required disclosure IS present in the text you were shown.',
